        Changelog
        ---------
        
        Unreleased
        ~~~~~~~~~~
        
        0.0.3 (2015-08-24)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Adds compatibility with onegov.core 0.4.25
          [href]
        
        0.0.2 (2015-08-18)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Renames 'academic_title' to the more general 'salutation'. This requires
          a onegov-core upgrade run to migrate existing databases.
          [href]
        
        - Removes Gravatar support.
          [href]
        
        0.0.1 (2015-07-03)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Initial Release
        
